items.title: How Fortune 500 Europe’s C-suite execs spend their time when they’re not hard at work—from puzzle-solving to jumping rope
items.description: From mind-bending puzzles to sports, Fortune 500 Europe's C-suite execs have many interests. The common thread? It makes them better leaders, they say...

items.title: Trump just asked the Supreme Court to delay the national TikTok ban so he can weigh in on it after he takes office
items.description: Trump has reversed his position on the popular app, having tried to ban it during his first term in office.

items.title: Donald Trump asks Supreme Court to pause looming TikTok ban so he can use his ‘dealmaking expertise’ to negotiate a resolution
items.description: Trump said the court should give him time after his Jan. 20 inauguration to “seek a negotiated resolution” of the dispute.
